des: Welcome to Blue Origin, the company dedicated to enabling a bright future where millions of people can live and work in space. Today, we’re launching New Shepard, a reusable rocket that takes science payloads, and soon human astronauts, to space. Experience a journey to space and back with New Shepard, and test your knowledge of reusable rocket systems as you meet experts from Blue's world-class engineering teams. Check back regularly as new mission parameters are being added.
